Package: presdown
Title: Build a directory of presentations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Steph", "Locke", 
         email = "steph@itsalocke.com", 
         role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Manage `rmarkdown` presentations 
         and turn them into directories of
         `markdown` and/or `HTML` files for
         incorporation into a larger site.
         Designed to be continuous integration
         friendly and do incremental commits to
         GitHub.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: covr,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
